<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zài gǔ zhōng wǒ yù jiàn nǐ, nǐ shì shèng jié de bǎi hé huā,
 zài yuán zhōng wǒ yù jiàn nǐ, nǐ shì xiān hóng de fèng xiān huā,
 zài shā lún wǒ yù jiàn nǐ, nǐ shì fēn fāng de méi guī huā,
 xiāng màn tiān yá, ài yáng tiān xià, zhǔ nǐ shì wǒ men pàn wàng de mí sài yà,
 yī wǒ shāng tòng, tì wǒ shòu xíng fá, jīn shēng jīn shì, wǒ bù zài jù pà
 rén shēng chōng mǎn nǐ de tóng zài shēng mìng lǐ rán qǐ bù miè de huǒ huā.</lyrics>
<title>zài gǔ zhōng wǒ yù jiàn nǐ 迦南473</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
